{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bff241fbd2","title":"在上海会议上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"51bade1c55","index":0,"year":1960,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"bff241fbd2","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji43","name":"毛泽东全集第43卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/43-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji43":{"comments":[{"id":"73fa5b9317","publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"bff241fbd2","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东在上海召开的中共中央政治局会议上讲话的摘录。"}],"contents":[{"id":"38f7431849","type":"title","text":"在上海会议上的讲话叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"bff241fbd2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"73fa5b9317","type":"paragraph","text":"人类历史一百来万年中，资产阶级统治的三百年是一个大跃进资产阶级都能够实现大跃进，无产阶级为什么不能实现大跃进？现在，有些人不相信我们，是有理由的。你没有东西，人家怎么能够相信呢？要人家糊里糊涂相信我们，这是不能设想的。经过若干年，我们真正有了东西，而且经过多次反复，他们才会相信我们","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"bff241fbd2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b442033912","type":"paragraph","text":"要长期保持大跃进，必须搞好工农业的比例关系。这一套两条腿走路中，工农业的比例关系是最主要的。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"bff241fbd2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6bd937798e","type":"paragraph","text":"（一月九日）","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"bff241fbd2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5d9024828c","type":"paragraph","text":"我们能够管六亿多人口，其他地方我们都管不了。有些地方有我们的使馆，可以进行一切可以进行的活动，但是，也不等于我们能够当他们的参课长。我们不能当美、英的参谋长，也不能当苏联的参谋长。要分几个阶段，我们的国家搞强大起来，我们的人民搞进步起来，争取我们的经济接近美国和苏联那个时候的水平。这主要靠自己把工作做好。我们的工作重点是争取人民，包括工人、农民、革命知识分子、革命的民族资产阶级。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"bff241fbd2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"da3ec7af3a","type":"paragraph","text":"（一月十七日）","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"bff241fbd2","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":129,"end":129}}}},"__N_SSG":true}